To install this web serivce:

1. First install all prerequisites for ERMrest

   See https://confluence.misd.isi.edu:8443/display/MISD/ERMrest+Installation

2. Install Globus Online Transfer Client API

   'easy_install globusonline-transfer-api-client'

3. Install this package

   'python setup.py install'

4. Optionally, create the static dir

   'mkdir -p /var/www/html/microscopy/static'

5. Install the wsgi configuration

   'cp wsgi_microscopy.conf /etc/httpd/conf.d'

6. Update your httpd/conf with directives matching or similar to the examples

   'cat examples/httpd.conf'

7. Update your httpd/conf.d/ssl.conf with directives matching or similar to

   'cat examples/ssl.conf'

8. Restart httpd

   'service httpd restart'